Flow
 Driver -> notifies current location and availability
 Passenger -> see all nearby drivers
 Customer  -> request a ride, near by drivers are notified
 on mutual acceptance of driver and customer of a ride, both can see location until trip finishes
 On completion driver marks journey to be available for next ride

 Capacity estimation
  --100 million registerd users and 1 million drivers
  -- 1 million active drivers and 500K daily users
  -- 1 million daily rides
  -- all active driver notify there location
  -- Customer puts a request for ride,system should be able to contact drivers real time
